Hubert Willis https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hubert_Willis 0 Hubert Willis (1876 in Reading, Berkshire, UK – 13 December 1933) was a British actor. He was best known for his recurring role as Doctor Watson in a series of silent Sherlock Holmes films co-starring with Eille Norwood.
